ca.cgjennings.ui.textedit

Enum TokenType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TokenType>
      • ca.cgjennings.ui.textedit.TokenType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TokenType>

    public enum TokenType
extends Enum<TokenType>
    An enumeration of the possible Token types. A token type is a generic syntactic category that may play a similar role in a variety of supported languages.
    Since:
    3.0
